text:
Hi there, I’m a Brand Strategist / Creative hybrid and a former Marketing VP. My friend Sandy (Alexandra Barrera) invited me to this channel and I am just now getting on. Hope to make contacts for work here and partner with other freelancers in different disciplines to land client work as well.

I specialize in authentic brand stories, rebranding, content strategy, planning, messaging including writing and editing as well as brand documentary story direction (used to own a brand documentary company with clients like Comcast NBCU, Timex, and Beyond Meat). I am starting a new column on Inc. in a few days on Authentic Marketing. Nice to meet everyone.
